916
02:02:59,544 --> 02:03:01,021
<font color="#ffff00">1, 2, 3.</font>

917
02:03:01,056 --> 02:03:02,700
<font color="#ffff00">Thả xuống.</font>

918
02:03:21,892 --> 02:03:24,189
<font color="#ffff00">- Anh ta sao rồi?
